8\t[OK] OTLP: Node.js packages installed\n309\t\n310\t── Observability ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n311\t[WARN] Port 9428 already in use\n312\t       → Shared stack may be running from another project\n313\t       → Check: docker compose -p codeharness-shared ps"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_017yeHkU1PuPSZdAjtPbsbrV","session_id":"5e9a7eca-0e0b-47b2-8610-117311a6629c","uuid":"1e06317d-06e9-4df1-a797-4cca7bffa2b0","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:28:03.735Z"}
