{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PG56JCWATqNNCSPWvZhNZL","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Harness Cost Report\n2\t\n3\tTotal API-equivalent cost: $15.37\n4\tTotal API calls: 119\n5\tAverage cost per story: $6.91 (2 stories)\n6\t\n7\t## Cost by Token Type\n8\t\n9\t| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n10\t|------|--------|------|------|---|\n11\t| Cache reads | 6,796,708 | $1.50/MTok | $10.20 | 66% |\n12\t| Cache writes | 160,732 | $18.75/MTok | $3.01 | 20% |\n13\t| Output | 28,821 | $75/MTok | $2.16 | 14% |\n14\t| Input | 127 | $15/MTok | $0.00 | 0% |\n15\t\n16\t## Cost by Phase\n17\t\n18\t| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n19\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n20\t| verify | 67 | $8.31 | 54.1% |\n21\t| orchestrator | 11 | $2.28 | 14.8% |\n22\t| create-story | 17 | $1.77 | 11.5% |\n23\t| dev-story | 10 | $1.19 | 7.8% |\n24\t| code-review | 9 | $1.04 | 6.8% |\n25\t| retro | 5 | $0.78 | 5.0% |\n26\t\n27\t## Cost by Tool\n28\t\n29\t| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n30\t|------|-------|------|---|\n31\t| Bash | 34 | $3.91 | 25.4% |\n32\t| Read | 30 | $3.57 | 23.2% |\n33\t| Edit | 25 | $3.11 | 20.3% |\n34\t| Agent | 14 | $2.12 | 13.8% |\n35\t| Grep | 9 | $1.03 | 6.7% |\n36\t| Skill | 2 | $0.75 | 4.9% |\n37\t| Glob | 3 | $0.67 | 4.4% |\n38\t| Write | 2 | $0.21 | 1.4% |\n39\t\n40\t## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n41\t\n42\t| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n43\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n44\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 68 | $8.34 | 54.2% |\n45\t| 1-3-workflow-state-module | 47 | $5.48 | 35.6% |\n46\t| unknown | 4 | $1.56 | 10.1% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PAev56xh5KBVmmNBmbCvca","session_id":"5e9a7eca-0e0b-47b2-8610-117311a6629c","uuid":"c86f07b1-a13b-4257-a38d-e38a1bee0dd3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:44:27.190Z"}
