{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JggGAwYQZmHM6yyiqrfKqY","type":"tool_result","content":"298\t\n299\t### Patterns to Avoid\n300\t\n301\t- **Running coverage commands multiple times per phase.** Dev-story ran it 3x, code-review tried grep 3x. Establish a pattern: run once, capture output, parse from captured output.\n302\t- **Deleting data sources before saving their data.** Story 1-2 deleted ralph/session-logs before `codeharness stats --save` could run. Always save before delete.\n303\t- **Relying on ANSI-aware parsing for coverage output.** Either strip ANSI at the source (run with `--no-color`) or build a robust strip function.\n304\t\n305\t---\n306\t\n307\t## 7. Action Items\n308\t\n309\t| # | Action | Priority | Owner | Status |\n310\t|---|--------|----------|-------|--------|\n311\t| 1 | Fix `codeharness stats` to handle missing session-logs directory | HIGH | Standalone fix or Epic 5 | Carried from Session 1 |\n312\t| 2 | Fix `package.json` `files` array — remove stale `ralph/**/*.sh` and `ralph/AGENTS.md` entries | HIGH | Next session | Carried from Session 1 |\n313\t| 3 | Clean up stale AGENTS.md entries from stories 1-1/1-2 | LOW | Tech debt | New |\n314\t| 4 | Add `--no-color` flag to all `vitest --coverage` invocations in subagent prompts | MEDIUM | Process improvement | New |\n315\t| 5 | Establish \"run coverage once, parse from captured output\" pattern in dev-story skill | MEDIUM | Process improvement | New |\n316\t| 6 | Begin Epic 2 (workflow YAML schema and parser) | HIGH | Next sprint session | New |\n317\t| 7 | Consider adding true cross-process persistence test for workflow-state (spawn child process) | LOW | Tech debt | New |\n318\t\n319\t---\n320\t\n321\t### Epic 1 Final Scorecard\n322\t\n323\t| Story | Tool Calls | Key Issues Found | Outcome |\n324\t|-------|-----------|-----------------|---------|\n325\t| 1-1-delete-beads-integration | ~119 | Dead type members, stale JSDoc | done |\n326\t| 1-2-delete-ralph-loop-legacy-verification | ~114 | Incomplete ralph/ deletion, broken stats.ts path | done |\n327\t| 1-3-workflow-state-module | 74 | Naming collision, validation gaps | done |\n328\t| **Epic Total** | **~307** | 8 issues found by review | **DONE** |\n329\t\n330\tEpic 1 achieved its goal: remove legacy subsystems (beads, ralph, legacy verification) and establish the first v2 module (workflow-state). The codebase is cleaner (-656K LOC from ralph alone) and ready for Epic 2.\n331\t\n332\t---\n333\t\n334\t# Session Retrospective — 2026-04-02 (Session 3: Story 2-1 + Full-Day Rollup)\n335\t\n336\t**Generated:** 2026-04-02T15:05 UTC\n337\t\n338\t## 1. Session Summary\n339\t\n340\t**Date:** 2026-04-02\n341\t**Stories attempted this session:** 1\n342\t**Stories completed this session:** 1\n343\t**Full-day stories completed:** 4 (1-1, 1-2, 1-3, 2-1)\n344\t\n345\t| Story | Phases Run | Outcome | Notes |\n346\t|-------|-----------|---------|-------|\n347\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | create-story, dev-story, code-review, verification | done | First Epic 2 story; JSON Schema + ajv validation |\n348\t\n349\t**Sprint progress after session:** Epic 1 fully done (3/3). Epic 2 started — story 2-1 done, 2-2 through 2-5 remain in backlog.\n350\t\n351\t---\n352\t\n353\t## 2. Issues Analysis\n354\t\n355\t### Issues from Story 2-1 (from .session-issues.md)\n356\t\n357\t**Spec/Config Gaps (3)**\n358\t- `_bmad/bmm/config.yaml` does not exist — create-story agent inferred config from file locations.\n359\t- Technical workflow engine research document referenced in epics-v2.md does not exist locally.\n360\t- Implementation artifact paths inferred, not read from a config source.\n361\t\n362\t**Code Quality Issues Found by Review (2)**\n363\t- **HIGH (fixed):** Branch coverage 75% on `schema-validate.ts` — `??` fallback paths in error mapping never tested. Review added 4 fake validator tests to reach 100% branch coverage.\n364\t- **MEDIUM (fixed):** `require()` calls in ESM test file — replaced with fake validator pattern.\n365\t\n366\t**Deferred Items (2)**\n367\t- **LOW:** No barrel re-export for `schema-validate.ts` — downstream imports directly. Not blocking.\n368\t- **LOW:** Module-level Ajv singleton pays compilation cost at import time. Negligible for CLI usage.\n369\t\n370\t**Naming Deviation (1)**\n371\t- Story spec said `validateWorkflowYaml` but dev used `validateWorkflowSchema` — function validates parsed JS objects, not YAML strings. Pragmatically correct but diverges from spec.\n372\t\n373\t**ajv Dependency Decision (1)**\n374\t- Story spec said dev-time cost, but validation runs at CLI runtime (story 2-5 `validate` command), so `ajv` was correctly added as a production dependency.\n375\t\n376\t**Verification Format Problems (1)**\n377\t- Proof document required 3 rewrites: wrong headers (`### AC` instead of `## AC`), then missing evidence format (needs `bash`+`output` code blocks), then finally correct. This is the same format issue seen in Sessions 1 and 2 — it remains unfixed in subagent instructions.\n378\t\n379\t### Severity Distribution\n380\t\n381\t| Severity | Count | Fixed? |\n382\t|----------|-------|--------|\n383\t| HIGH | 1 | Yes (branch coverage) |\n384\t| MEDIUM | 1 | Yes (ESM require) |\n385\t| LOW | 3 | Deferred |\n386\t\n387\t---\n388\t\n389\t## 3. Cost Analysis\n390\t\n391\t### This Session (Story 2-1 + orchestrator overhead)\n392\t\n393\tFrom `codeharness stats --save`:\n394\t\n395\t**Total cost: $15.37** across 119 API calls (covers stories 2-1 and 1-3 in current tracking window).\n396\t\n397\t**Cost by Phase:**\n398\t\n399\t| Phase | Calls | Cost | % of Total |\n400\t|-------|-------|------|------------|\n401\t| verify | 67 | $8.31 | 54.1% |\n402\t| orchestrator | 11 | $2.28 | 14.8% |\n403\t| create-story | 17 | $1.77 | 11.5% |\n404\t| dev-story | 10 | $1.19 | 7.8% |\n405\t| code-review | 9 | $1.04 | 6.8% |\n406\t| retro | 5 | $0.78 | 5.0% |\n407\t\n408\t**Cost by Story:**\n409\t\n410\t| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n411\t|-------|-------|------|---|\n412\t| 2-1-workflow-yaml-json-schema | 68 | $8.34 | 54.2% |\n413\t| 1-3-workflow-state-module | 47 | $5.48 | 35.6% |\n414\t| unknown (orchestrator overhead) | 4 | $1.56 | 10.1% |\n415\t\n416\t**Cost by Token Type:**\n417\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PAev56xh5KBVmmNBmbCvca","session_id":"5e9a7eca-0e0b-47b2-8610-117311a6629c","uuid":"360971f1-dac7-4709-868a-fe65002a35ae","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:44:45.168Z"}
