t assertion. No ambiguity, no judgment calls.\n926\t\n927\t### Patterns to Avoid\n928\t\n929\t- **Carrying action items across 5 sessions without fixing them.** The ANSI color code issue, `codeharness stats` breakage, and `package.json` stale entries have been carried since Sessions 1-2. The accumulated waste from ANSI retries alone is ~15-20 wasted tool calls across the day.\n930\t- **Not stripping ANSI codes at source.** Every session loses 3-5 calls to ANSI grep failures. One `--no-color` flag eliminates all of them.\n931\t- **Running npm test twice in verification.** A single `npm test` run should suffice unless the first run reveals failures.\n932\t\n933\t---\n934\t\n935\t## 7. Action Items\n936\t\n937\t| # | Action | Priority | Status |\n938\t|---|--------|----------|--------|\n939\t| 1 | **FIX: Add proof format specification to verification skill prompt** | CRITICAL | Carried x4 — improvement seen (3x -> 1x retries) but still not fixed at source |\n940\t| 2 | **FIX: `codeharness stats` to handle missing session-logs directory** | HIGH | Carried x4 |\n941\t| 3 | Fix `package.json` `files` array — remove stale `ralph/**/*.sh` and `ralph/AGENTS.md` | HIGH | Carried x4 |\n942\t| 4 | Add `--no-color` to vitest invocations in subagent prompts | MEDIUM | Carried x3 — ~15-20 wasted calls today from ANSI issues |\n943\t| 5 | Fix pre-existing query metrics test failures (6 tests) | MEDIUM | Carried x1 |\n944\t| 6 | Remove or fix BATS integration tests referencing deleted shell scripts | MEDIUM | Carried x1 |\n945\t| 7 | Document `_bmad/config.yaml` location in project context | LOW | Carried x1 |\n946\t| 8 | Begin story 2-4-init-command-workflow-generation | HIGH | Next session |\n947\t\n948\t---\n949\t\n950\t## Full-Day Final Summary (2026-04-02, End of Day)\n951\t\n952\t### Stories Completed\n953\t\n954\t| # | Story | Epic | Type | Phases | Tool Calls | Key Review Findings |\n955\t|---|-------|------|------|--------|-----------|-------------------|\n956\t| 1 | 1-1-de